author: Paavo Nurmi
message: Mind is everything: muscle, pieces of rubber. All that I am, I am because of my mind.
title: Thought of the day

author: Anne Frank
message: How wonderful it is that nobody need wait a single moment before starting to improve the world.
title: Thought of the day

message: A friend is someone who understands your past, believes in your future, and accepts you just the way you are.
title: Thought of the day

author: Ralph Emerson
message: It is one of the blessings of old friends that you can afford to be stupid with them.
title: Thought of the day
